@@ -1250,7 +1453,9 @@ static HB_ERRCODE adsSeek( ADSAREAP pArea, HB_BOOL bSoftSeek, PHB_ITEM pKey, HB_
     * when it doesn't but only sometimes. I've not been able to detect
